
  build image: 

    - docker build -t img_run-env .
  
  run a container from the image:
  
    - docker run -itd --name cont_run-env img_run-env
 
  execute the container bash command:

   -  docker exec -it cont_run-env bash

 after that the shell of container is running interactively:
  
        root@d0b143d26dc0:/# echo $USER
	   Cerulean-Canvas
	root@d0b143d26dc0:/# echo $SHELL
	   /bin/bash
	root@d0b143d26dc0:/# echo $LOGNAME
	   Cerulean-Canvas
	root@d0b143d26dc0:/# cd /home/
	root@d0b143d26dc0:/home# ls
	   Codes
	root@d0b143d26dc0:/home# exit
	   exit
 

